dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Barron County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data layers represent roads and right of way (ROW) for Barron County in 2018. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Barron_Roads_ROW_2018.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'BARRON_ROADS_2017' and 'BARRON_ROW_2018'.
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: Barron County Land Information/Surveyor/Real Property Lister
